_:c4221a13fe47a6c39f689b84a83f63ca a <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E52_Time-span> ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P78_is_identified_by> "He was the seventh head  of the monastery of Dabra Libānos\n                  who succeeded his predecessor\n                   \n                     ʾabuna  Yoḥannǝs Sǝwwur and he was a contemporary \n                  of King \n                     Yǝsḥaq. His tenure was remarkable for the development of the monastery of Dabra Libānos and its literature. \n\n                  It is believed that Gadla Filǝṗṗos\n                  of  \n                  \n                    ʾabuna Filǝṗṗos was written during his tenure.\n                 " .
